No. 269,

Misc.

No. 275,

Misc.

Conley v. Green, Superintendent, Marion Correctional Institution; and Eineder v. Bannan, Warden.

Motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as petitions for writs of certiorari, certiorari is denied. Mr. Justice Stewart took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
